snippet.title: छत पर इतने सारे आम गमले में ऐसे उगाता हूँ ग्राफ्टिंग से ~How to grow mango tree from seed and graf
snippet.description:
How to grow mango tree in pot. Mango grafting trick with 2 Year's Updates from seed to harvest. The only video on internet, from growing seed to harvesting mangoes in pot. Everyone is crazy about the taste of mangoes. No wonder it is called the king of fruits. This video is all about growing lots of mangoes in the pot. I will demonstrate 2 easiest methods to grow mangoes. first by mango seed. And in the second method, I'll show the complete technique of grafting seed grown mango plant, I will also grow a lot of mangoes in the grafted tree with 3 years of updates. Which varieties can be grown in a pot. How to take care of it. You will get the details of all these in a single video.
